What are the specific self-care strategies mentioned in the evidence-based article from the Journal of Behavioral Medicine that have been proven effective in improving mental health outcomes among individuals dealing with the stressors of COVID-19 pandemic? Please provide the summarized findings along with the JSON data.
Here is the summarized findings and corresponding JSON data:
The article suggests that physical exercise, relaxation techniques, and cognitive-behavioral interventions are effective self-care strategies for improving mental health outcomes during the COVID-19 pandemic. The study also found that regular exercise can help reduce stress, anxiety, and depression. According to the JSON data, the specific self-care strategies recommended are as follows:
